2.10	Bromargyrite	Bromargyrite	Bromyrite or bromargyrite is a natural mineral form of silver bromide found mainly in Mexico and Chile. Hardness is 1.5 to 2. Related are chlorargyrite and iodyrite.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0b/Bromargyrit_mit_gediegen_Silber_-_San_Onofre%2C_Mexiko.jpg/240px-Bromargyrit_mit_gediegen_Silber_-_San_Onofre%2C_Mexiko.jpg
